      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/extreme-bond-market-shorts-gamble-on-a-hawkish-powell-pivot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在许多人预计美联储将采取鹰派立场之前，受到市场近期暴跌打击的债券交易员变得越来越悲观。]]></description>
